{"tid":502802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好怕再識新朋友，點解自己會咁","createTime":"2017-12-18T09:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T05:44:22.000Z","uid":45439,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b361053c6fc02fa5500282fdedb658451ab51579","tid":502802,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"好驚再識新朋友，識耐左人地發掘你缺點就會疏遠你變無咁frd 。好怕有交際活動，黎黎去去都係打牌打啤牌但自己唔識玩呢啲，所以好怕social同埋驚俾人笑你唔識打牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到長遠落去而家成日都係自己一個人食飯,自己一個人睇戲,自己一個人去做gym，黎緊仲會一個人去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人係咁，我諗我真係異類啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我21歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04c308b5ce792249c4b4950f92f0b66228e8771","tid":502802,"uid":41737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91dc83488f843a0bba19cbc7e9fec8b200ac3d8c","tid":502802,"uid":3908,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aad4c7176c6cd2632c9bac1ab44e88bc784d4c9a","tid":502802,"uid":108394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"有時一個人係幾爽嘅 但持續太耐就變得唔好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1b5d5f6ff2be069bf44ea36f02bce6019248bd","tid":502802,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩缺點</blockquote><br />\n可能人地同我溝通會覺得好難有話題，所以我識親朋友一開始fd/ok，慢慢就淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93798b3b785ebd47f315ae477db8923817e2f54","tid":502802,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime